    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">Jamuna: In the earlier days we used to keep moving around and
            continue doing our work and give birth to our babies as a routine matter. We would
            go to work in the fields and have our babies there itself. We would cut the <i>naal
            </i>with a knife that was at hand. We would wrap our <em>ghagra</em> (long skirt)
