    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">Teeja: In our village there were two women in one house. They
            were <em>Devrani</em> and <em>Jethani</em>. The <em>Devrani</em> was expecting a
            baby. She was in her seventh month. She had gone to work in the fields. She gave
            birth there itself. She cut her own cord. She wrapped her baby in cloth and came
