            five rupees. This is called <em>kansa</em> <em>dena</em>. Some <i>dais</i> don&#8217;t
            like to eat there. They prefer to take the food home. </span>
    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">On <em>Suraj</em> <em>puja</em> day, the house gets cleaned. Some
