    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">Rukma: Before the baby is born, if there is water discharge, we
            give coconut ground and boiled in milk. This prevents further leakage of water.
        </span>
    </p>
    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">Jhinkar: I had no help during the birth of my third baby. I was
