    <p align="justify">
        <span class="default">Satyanarayanji: I had gone to work with this organisation which
            is dealing with mother and child health. This is Dr.Keerti Iyengar&#8217;s organisation.
            They are trying to train intermediary people between nurses and doctors who can
            operate technical equipment at different centres that they plan to open. They also
